LU-16499 lfs: Add directory argument support to lfs migrate

this patch adds support for directory arguments to lfs migrate
command, matching the functionality of lfs_migrate script.

This allows commands like:
 lfs migrate -c 2 /path/to/directory

Test-Parameters: trivial

